Sys/MemInfo version 0.04
========================

This module return the total amount of free and used physical memory
in bytes in totalmem and freemem variables.

This module has been tested on Linux, OpenUnix, AIX5, OpenBSD, HPUX11,
Tru64 5.1 and Windows XP.

It should work on Solaris, Windows Server 2003 and others *bsd systems
like FreeBSD and NetBSD.

INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   make install

if you get some troubles with MS Windows take a look on 
http://www.netsack.net/index.php?url=uggc%2Sjjj.creyzbaxf.bet%2S%3Sabqr_vq%3Q510773

DEPENDENCIES

This module requires these other modules and libraries:

  File::Copy

